data.description: Hello Verdigris!! The light and bright feel of this home, wood burning fireplace and spacious yard will have you coming home every day to pure joy...or maybe make you not want to leave! The peaceful neighborhood and convenience to all of Claremore, Catoosa, Owasso and Tulsa make it an ideal location for work and play. There are so many boxes that get checked with this house! You will love calling it HOME!
